    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a masterpiece of automotive poetry. This isn't merely a vehicle; it is a preserved moment of engineering perfection, radiating the kind of timeless grace that stops traffic and starts conversations. The cabin greets you with the scent of heritage leather, untouched by the passage of years, while the exterior gleams with a luster so deep it feels like you could dive into the paintwork. Every curve hums with the promise of open roads and sun-drenched afternoons. To drive this is to command a symphony of chrome and soul, a rare opportunity for the connoisseur who demands nothing less than a legend in its prime.",
      "price": 46500.0,
